channel.description:
Hello Star Wars Fans! My name is Krister. I run the Star Wars YouTube Channel "StarGeek", bringing you content every week about all of your favorite Star Wars subjects. Some of my series include 'Star Wars Factor Beam', where I present five Star Wars facts that you can't pull away from on different characters/films/categories. 'Top Ten' videos are also abundant on the channel, featuring every topic you could possibly think of. Reviews are some of my favorites, from The Force Awakens to the 80's cartoons and Holiday Special. 'Music Videos' and 'VERSUS' episodes also pop up every once in a while! You can always suggest videos to me if you have any new ideas! Don't forget to SUBSCRIBE to become one of the STAR WARRIORS, and receive Star Wars content every week. Until we meet again in a galaxy far, far away, this has been STAR GEEK.

-Star Geek
